<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Slab — Your Website, Built by AI, Live in Minutes</title>
  <meta name="description" content="Full website platform with AI content agents, client management, invoicing, and email campaigns. Free to start, $50/mo to go live.">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    :root {
      --gold: #c9a848;
      --dark: #0a0a0a;
      --card: #141414;
      --border: #262626;
      --muted: #737373;
      --light: #e5e5e5;
    }
    * { margin:0; padding:0; box-sizing:border-box; }
    body { font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; background:var(--dark); color:var(--light); overflow-x:hidden; }
    a { color:var(--gold); text-decoration:none; }

    /* ── Nav ── */
    .nav { position:fixed; top:0; left:0; right:0; z-index:100; padding:16px 32px; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:space-between; background:rgba(10,10,10,0.85); backdrop-filter:blur(12px); border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.04); }
    .nav-logo { font-size:22px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; } .nav-logo span { color:var(--gold); }
    .nav-links { display:flex; gap:28px; align-items:center; }
    .nav-links a { font-size:13px; color:#a3a3a3; transition:color 0.2s; } .nav-links a:hover { color:#fff; }
    .nav-cta { background:var(--gold); color:var(--dark); padding:8px 20px; border-radius:6px; font-weight:600; font-size:13px; }
    .nav-cta:hover { background:#d4b85c; }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .hero { min-height:100vh; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; text-align:center; padding:120px 24px 80px; position:relative; }
    .hero::before { content:''; position:absolute; top:0; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); width:600px; height:600px; background:radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,168,72,0.08) 0%, transparent 70%); pointer-events:none; }
    .hero-content { max-width:720px; position:relative; }
    .hero-badge { display:inline-block; font-size:11px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px; color:var(--gold); background:rgba(201,168,72,0.1); border:1px solid rgba(201,168,72,0.2); padding:6px 16px; border-radius:20px; margin-bottom:24px; }
    .hero h1 { font-size:clamp(36px, 6vw, 64px); font-weight:800; line-height:1.1; letter-spacing:-1.5px; color:#fff; margin-bottom:20px; }
    .hero h1 em { font-style:normal; color:var(--gold); }
    .hero p { font-size:18px; color:#a3a3a3; line-height:1.7; max-width:540px; margin:0 auto 36px; }
    .hero-actions { display:flex; gap:12px; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap; }
    .btn-lg { padding:16px 36px; border-radius:8px; font-family:'Inter',sans-serif; font-size:15px; font-weight:600; border:none; cursor:pointer; transition:all 0.2s; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block; }
    .btn-primary { background:var(--gold); color:var(--dark); } .btn-primary:hover { background:#d4b85c; transform:translateY(-1px); }
    .btn-outline { background:transparent; color:#fff; border:1px solid #333; } .btn-outline:hover { border-color:var(--gold); }

    /* ── Features ── */
    .features { padding:80px 24px; }
    .features-inner { max-width:1000px; margin:0 auto; }
    .section-label { font-size:11px; text-transform:uppercase; letter-spacing:2px; color:var(--gold); text-align:center; margin-bottom:8px; }
    .section-title { font-size:32px; font-weight:700; text-align:center; color:#fff; margin-bottom:48px; letter-spacing:-0.5px; }
    .feature-grid { display:grid; grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr)); gap:20px; }
    .feature-card { background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:10px; padding:28px; transition:border-color 0.3s; }
    .feature-card:hover { border-color:rgba(201,168,72,0.3); }
    .feature-icon { font-size:28px; margin-bottom:12px; }
    .feature-card h3 { font-size:16px; font-weight:600; margin-bottom:8px; color:#fff; }
    .feature-card p { font-size:13px; color:#a3a3a3; line-height:1.6; }

    /* ── How it works ── */
    .how { padding:80px 24px; background:var(--card); border-top:1px solid var(--border); border-bottom:1px solid var(--border); }
    .how-inner { max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; }
    .steps { display:grid; gap:32px; margin-top:48px; }
    .step { display:flex; gap:20px; align-items:flex-start; }
    .step-num { width:40px; height:40px; border-radius:50%; background:rgba(201,168,72,0.1); border:1px solid rgba(201,168,72,0.3); display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center; font-size:16px; font-weight:700; color:var(--gold); flex-shrink:0; }
    .step-text h3 { font-size:16px; font-weight:600; color:#fff; margin-bottom:4px; }
    .step-text p { font-size:13px; color:#a3a3a3; line-height:1.6; }

    /* ── Pricing ── */
    .pricing { padding:80px 24px; }
    .pricing-inner { max-width:500px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center; }
    .price-card { background:var(--card); border:1px solid var(--border); border-radius:12px; padding:40px; margin-top:40px; }
    .price-amount { font-size:56px; font-weight:800; color:#fff; line-height:1; }
    .price-amount span { font-size:18px; font-weight:400; color:var(--muted); }
    .price-desc { font-size:14px; color:#a3a3a3; margin:12px 0 24px; }
    .price-features { list-style:none; text-align:left; margin-bottom:28px; }
    .price-features li { font-size:13px; color:#d4d4d4; padding:8px 0; border-bottom:1px solid #1f1f1f; display:flex; align-items:center; gap:10px; }
    .price-features li::before { content:''; width:6px; height:6px; border-radius:50%; background:var(--gold); flex-shrink:0; }
    .free-note { font-size:12px; color:var(--muted); margin-top:12px; }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .cta { padding:80px 24px; text-align:center; }
    .cta h2 { font-size:32px; font-weight:700; color:#fff; margin-bottom:12px; }
    .cta p { font-size:16px; color:#a3a3a3; margin-bottom:28px; }

    /* ── Footer ── */
    .footer { padding:32px 24px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); text-align:center; font-size:12px; color:#525252; }

    @media (max-width:640px) {
      .nav { padding:12px 16px; }
      .nav-links a:not(.nav-cta) { display:none; }
      .hero { padding:100px 16px 60px; }
      .feature-grid { grid-template-columns:1fr; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="nav">
  <div class="nav-logo"><span>S</span>lab</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#features">Features</a>
    <a href="#how">How It Works</a>
    <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="/superadmin/login">Admin</a>
    <a href="/start" class="nav-cta">Get Started Free</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero-content">
    <div class="hero-badge">AI-Powered Website Platform</div>
    <h1>Your website, <em>built by AI</em>, live in minutes</h1>
    <p>Full website with admin panel, AI content agents, client management, invoicing, and email campaigns. Build for free. Go live when you're ready.</p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="/start" class="btn-lg btn-primary">Start Building — Free</a>
      <a href="#how" class="btn-lg btn-outline">See How It Works</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="features" id="features">
  <div class="features-inner">
    <div class="section-label">Everything Included</div>
    <div class="section-title">One platform, zero hassle</div>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#9672;</div>
        <h3>AI Content Agents</h3>
        <p>Five specialist AI agents write your copy, blog posts, design tokens, and page content. Just tell them what you need.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#9670;</div>
        <h3>Full Admin Panel</h3>
        <p>Manage every aspect of your site from one dashboard. Copy, design, portfolio, blog, pages — all editable in real time.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#9671;</div>
        <h3>Client Management</h3>
        <p>Track clients, send invoices, manage onboarding. Accept payments via Stripe and PayPal.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#9673;</div>
        <h3>Email Campaigns</h3>
        <p>Built-in email marketing with contact management, campaign builder, open/click tracking, and AI-written content.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#9674;</div>
        <h3>Video Meetings</h3>
        <p>Peer-to-peer video calls with shared notes, file uploads, and AI-powered meeting summaries. No Zoom needed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="feature-card">
        <div class="feature-icon">&#9675;</div>
        <h3>Custom Domain</h3>
        <p>Start on a free subdomain. When you're ready, connect your own domain with automatic SSL — we handle the setup.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="how" id="how">
  <div class="how-inner">
    <div class="section-label">Simple Setup</div>
    <div class="section-title">Live in three steps</div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-text">
          <h3>Sign up free</h3>
          <p>Pick a name, choose your URL. No credit card. Your admin panel is ready instantly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-text">
          <h3>Build your site</h3>
          <p>Use the AI agents to write your copy, create blog posts, set your brand colors and fonts. Preview everything before going live.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-text">
          <h3>Go live</h3>
          <p>When it looks right, hit Go Live. Your site is public at $50/month. Add a custom domain anytime.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="pricing" id="pricing">
  <div class="pricing-inner">
    <div class="section-label">Simple Pricing</div>
    <div class="section-title">One plan, everything included</div>
    <div class="price-card">
      <div class="price-amount">$50<span>/mo</span></div>
      <p class="price-desc">Everything you need to run your business online</p>
      <ul class="price-features">
        <li>Full website with custom design</li>
        <li>5 AI content agents</li>
        <li>Unlimited blog posts &amp; pages</li>
        <li>Client management &amp; invoicing</li>
        <li>Email marketing campaigns</li>
        <li>Video meetings</li>
        <li>Stripe &amp; PayPal payments</li>
        <li>Custom domain + SSL</li>
        <li>Google reviews integration</li>
      </ul>
      <a href="/start" class="btn-lg btn-primary" style="width:100%;text-align:center;">Start Building — Free</a>
      <p class="free-note">Free to build. Only pay when you go live.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="cta">
  <h2>Ready to build?</h2>
  <p>Create your site in minutes. No credit card, no commitments.</p>
  <a href="/start" class="btn-lg btn-primary">Get Started Free</a>
</section>

<footer class="footer">
  &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> Slab &mdash; Built by MadLadsLab
</footer>

</body>
</html>
